des: Click the Enable button and say: “Open TytoCare Pairing Guide”. The TytoCare device must be paired with the TytoCare app before it’s ready to use. It is recommended to pair your device as soon as you receive it so that it’s ready when you need to perform an exam. This guide is supported on all Alexa smart speakers. It may also work on your Alexa app if Alexa is defined as the default assistant.
